<small><small><br>
</small></small></td></tr></tbody></table><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></span><table style="text-align: left; width: 823px; height: 305px;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr><td style="white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: top;"><br><table style="text-align: left; width: 277px; height: 73px;" border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><big><big><big><big><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(204, 204, 204);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><small><span style="color: rgb(255, 102, 0);"> &nbsp; Events</span></small><span style="color: rgb(204, 204, 204);"></span></span></big></big></big></big></td></tr></tbody></table><br><br><br></td><td><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt; text-align: center;" align="center"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">A &nbsp;Quarter-century of Aikido.</span></b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt; text-align: center;" align="center"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Six Teachers.</span></b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt; text-align: center;" align="center"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">One Special Event.</span></b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Celebrate
25 years of training excellence with the Makati Aikdio Club and take
part in a rare and exciting event that brings together six of the
country&#8217;s most experienced teachers, including one from <span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228711582_0"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228712231_0"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228786780_0" style="border-bottom: medium none; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 50%; -moz-background-clip: initial; -moz-background-origin: initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: initial;"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228880831_0" style="border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(0, 102, 204);"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1229595353_0">Japan</span></span></span></span></span> and one from the U.S. </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">For its <span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228711582_1"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228712231_1"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228786780_1" style="border-bottom: medium none; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 50%; -moz-background-clip: initial; -moz-background-origin: initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: initial;"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1229595353_1">25th anniversary</span></span></span></span>
class offering, experience two hours of intense, focused instruction
under six experienced teachers, each of whom will share his expertise
on a chosen martial theme: </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.75in; line-height: 14.4pt;"><small><small><strong><big><b>·</b></big></strong></small></small><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mitsuhiro Ito &#8211; Rotation of the Core Muscles</span> 
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.75in; line-height: 14.4pt;"><small><small><strong><big><b>·</b></big></strong></small></small><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Troy Nones &#8211; Wrist Rotation </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.75in; line-height: 14.4pt;"><small><small><strong><big><b>·</b></big></strong></small></small><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Billy De Leon &#8211; Destabilizing Uke </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.75in; line-height: 14.4pt;"><small><small><strong><big><b>·</b></big></strong></small></small><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Royce Coffee &#8211; Atemi </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.75in; line-height: 14.4pt;"><small><small><strong><big><b>·</b></big></strong></small></small><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Royce Reyes &#8211; Relaxed Shoulders </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.75in; line-height: 14.4pt;"><small><small><strong><big><b>·</b></big></strong></small></small><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dam Amaranto - Centering </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Founded
in 1983, the MAC is among the pioneers of Aikido in the Philippines and
considered a frontrunner in aikido training excellence. Over the years,
more than 2,000 students have trained with the club, with a number of
its alumni moving on to found their own clubs or become senior members
of overseas aikido clubs. </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Feel
free to invite others who may be interested in joining this special,
fun event. After class, reconnect with former classmates and meet new
ones over food and drinks at the club's traditional Christmas party.&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Class Details</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Date: <span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228711582_2"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228712231_2"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228786780_2"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1229595353_2">December 13</span></span></span></span>, 2008 </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Time: starts at 6:30pm </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Venue: Makati (Sports) Club basement </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Mat fee: P100 </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Christmas Party Details</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">The Bread Box <span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228711582_3"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228712231_3"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228786780_3"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1229595353_3">Restaurant</span></span></span></span><br>7615 Guijo Street , <span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228711582_4"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228712231_4"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1228786780_4"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1229595353_4">Makati City</span></span></span></span> </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Contribution - P100 fee at the gate </span>
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; line-height: 14.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; </span>
</p><br><br><br><p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font color="#3300cc" face="Arial,Helvetica,Univers,Zurich BT" size="-1"><span style="color: white;">**********************************************************************************************************</span></font></p></td></tr><tr><td style="white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: top;"></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>&nbsp;
